Scalar-Quote
============

Quote and spot differences in two strings in an human friendly manner.

This module is mostly useful for debugging purposes.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Test::More

